Name: center

Details:

Categories: Library

Syntax:

Types:

Function:
`FProperty center()`

Synopsis:

Description:
`center` defines __horizontal and vertical centered alignment__.
It sets the horzontal and vertical anchor to 50% of the width, respectively, the height of the current figure.
`center()` is equivalent to `anchor(0.5, 0.5)`.

Also see [BoxModel] and [anchor].

